#. <section class="sutta" id="an5.27"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.27:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.27:0.2"
msgid "3. Pañcaṅgikavagga"
msgstr "3. With Five Factors"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an5.27:0.3"
msgid "27. Samādhisutta"
msgstr "27. Immersion"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an5.27:1.1"
msgid "“Samādhiṃ, bhikkhave, bhāvetha appamāṇaṃ nipakā patissatā."
msgstr "“Mendicants, develop limitless immersion, disciplined and mindful."

msgctxt "an5.27:1.2"
msgid ""
"Samādhiṃ, bhikkhave, bhāvayataṃ appamāṇaṃ nipakānaṃ patissatānaṃ pañca "
"ñāṇāni paccattaññeva uppajjanti."
msgstr ""
"When you develop limitless immersion, disciplined and mindful, five "
"knowledges arise for you personally."

msgctxt "an5.27:1.3"
msgid "Katamāni pañca?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "an5.27:1.4"
msgid ""
"‘Ayaṃ samādhi paccuppannasukho ceva āyatiñca sukhavipāko’ti paccattaññeva "
"ñāṇaṃ uppajjati, "
msgstr ""
"‘This immersion is blissful now, and results in bliss in the future.’ … "

msgctxt "an5.27:1.5"
msgid "‘ayaṃ samādhi ariyo nirāmiso’ti paccattaññeva ñāṇaṃ uppajjati, "
msgstr "‘This immersion is noble and spiritual.’ … "

#. VAR: akāpurisasevito’ti → mahāpurisasevitoti (mr)
msgctxt "an5.27:1.6"
msgid "‘ayaṃ samādhi akāpurisasevito’ti paccattaññeva ñāṇaṃ uppajjati, "
msgstr "‘This immersion is not cultivated by corrupt people.’ … "

#. VAR: na sasaṅkhāraniggayhavāritagato’ti → na ca sasaṅkhāraniggayhavāritacatoti (bj) | na ca sasaṅkhāraniggayhavāritappattoti (s1-3) | na ca sasaṅkhāraniggayhavāritāvaṭoti (pts1) | na ca sasaṅkhāraniggayhavārivāvaṭoti (mr) | na sasaṅkhāraniggayhavāriyādhigatoti (?)
msgctxt "an5.27:1.7"
msgid ""
"‘ayaṃ samādhi santo paṇīto paṭippassaddhaladdho ekodibhāvādhigato, na "
"sasaṅkhāraniggayhavāritagato’ti paccattaññeva ñāṇaṃ uppajjati, "
msgstr ""
"‘This immersion is peaceful and sublime and tranquil and unified, not held "
"in place by forceful suppression.’ … "

#. VAR: sato vuṭṭhahāmī’ti → sato ca uṭṭhahāmīti (bj) | sato vuṭṭhahāmīti (s1-3, km) | so kho panāhaṃ imaṃ samādhiṃ satova samāpajjāmi satova vuṭṭhahāmīti (pts1)
msgctxt "an5.27:1.8"
msgid ""
"‘sato kho panāhaṃ imaṃ samāpajjāmi sato vuṭṭhahāmī’ti paccattaññeva ñāṇaṃ "
"uppajjati."
msgstr "‘I mindfully enter into and emerge from this immersion.’ …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an5.27:2.1"
msgid "Samādhiṃ, bhikkhave, bhāvetha appamāṇaṃ nipakā patissatā."
msgstr "Develop limitless immersion, disciplined and mindful."

msgctxt "an5.27:2.2"
msgid ""
"Samādhiṃ, bhikkhave, bhāvayataṃ appamāṇaṃ nipakānaṃ patissatānaṃ imāni pañca "
"ñāṇāni paccattaññeva uppajjantī”ti."
msgstr ""
"When you develop limitless immersion, disciplined and mindful, these five "
"knowledges arise for you personally.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.27:2.3"
msgid "Sattamaṃ."
msgstr ""
